🎯 10 Most Asked Computer Network Interview Questions (SYSTEM LEVEL)
1️⃣ How does video streaming work?

Uses chunking, CDN, buffering.

2️⃣ Why does buffering happen?

Data arrival slower than playback.

3️⃣ How does WhatsApp send messages?

Through central server using TCP.

4️⃣ What is client-server model?

Central server handles communication.

5️⃣ What is peer-to-peer?

Direct communication between nodes.

6️⃣ What is CDN?

Servers closer to user.

7️⃣ What is latency?

Delay in transmission.

8️⃣ What is throughput?

Actual data delivered.

9️⃣ What is packet loss?

Lost packets in transmission.

🔟 What is jitter?

Variation in delay.

